### =================================================================
### 1. АВТОРИЗАЦИЯ И ОБЩИЕ МЕТОДЫ
### =================================================================

### 1.1. Инфо (Healthcheck)
GET http://localhost:8080/_info

### 1.2. Dummy Login (Admin)
# @name adminLogin
POST http://localhost:8080/dummyLogin
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "admin" }

> {%
    client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.token);
%}

### 1.3. Dummy Login (User)
# @name userLogin
POST http://localhost:8080/dummyLogin
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "user" }

> {%
    client.global.set("userToken", response.body.token);
%}

### 1.4. Dummy Login (Ошибка 400 - Неверная роль)
POST http://localhost:8080/dummyLogin
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "super-hacker" }


### =================================================================
### 2. УПРАВЛЕНИЕ ПЕРЕГОВОРКАМИ (ROOMS)
### =================================================================

### 2.1. Создать переговорку (Позитив)
# @name createRoom
POST http://localhost:8080/rooms/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Neon Conference Room",
  "description": "High-tech room for startup pitches",
  "capacity": 12
}

> {%
    client.global.set("roomId", response.body.room.id);
%}

### 2.2. Список всех переговорок
GET http://localhost:8080/rooms/list
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 2.3. Ошибка 403: User пытается создать переговорку
POST http://localhost:8080/rooms/create
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Forbidden Room" }


### =================================================================
### 3. РАСПИСАНИЕ (SCHEDULES)
### =================================================================

### 3.1. Создать расписание (Позитив)
# Пн-Пт с 09:00 до 18:00
POST http://localhost:8080/rooms/{{roomId}}/schedule/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "{{roomId}}",
  "daysOfWeek": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "18:00"
}

### 3.2. Ошибка 409: Повторное создание расписания
POST http://localhost:8080/rooms/{{roomId}}/schedule/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "{{roomId}}",
  "daysOfWeek": [6, 7],
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

### 3.3. Ошибка 404: Расписание для несуществующей комнаты
POST http://localhost:8080/rooms/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/schedule/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "daysOfWeek": [1],
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "11:00"
}


### =================================================================
### 4. СЛОТЫ (SLOTS)
### =================================================================

### 4.1. Список слотов (Позитив - триггерит генерацию, если их нет)
# @name listSlots
GET http://localhost:8080/rooms/{{roomId}}/slots/list?date=2026-06-15
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

> {%
    if (response.body.slots && response.body.slots.length > 0) {
        client.global.set("slotId", response.body.slots[0].id);
        client.global.set("secondSlotId", response.body.slots[1].id);
    }
%}

### 4.2. Ошибка 400: Запрос списка слотов без даты
GET http://localhost:8080/rooms/{{roomId}}/slots/list
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### =================================================================
### 5. БРОНИРОВАНИЕ (BOOKINGS)
### =================================================================

### 5.1. Создать бронь (Позитив)
# @name createBooking
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings/create
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotId": "{{slotId}}",
  "createConferenceLink": true
}

> {%
    client.global.set("bookingId", response.body.booking.id);
%}

### 5.2. Ошибка 409: Слот уже занят
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings/create
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotId": "{{slotId}}"
}

### 5.3. Ошибка 403: Администратор не может бронировать
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotId": "{{secondSlotId}}"
}

### 5.4. Список своих броней (User) - Только будущие
GET http://localhost:8080/bookings/my
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 5.5. Список всех броней (Admin) + пагинация
GET http://localhost:8080/bookings/list?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### =================================================================
### 6. ОТМЕНА БРОНИ (CANCELLATION) И ИДЕМПОТЕНТНОСТЬ
### =================================================================

### 6.1. Отмена своей брони (Позитив)
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings/{{bookingId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 6.2. Идемпотентность: Повторная отмена той же брони (Должно быть 200 OK)
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings/{{bookingId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 6.3. Ошибка 404: Отмена несуществующей брони
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 6.4. Ошибка 401: Отмена без токена
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings/{{bookingId}}/cancel